criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  men and women aged ≥18 years;

          -  clinical diagnosis confirmed by common investigations to establish the presence of
             colon or lung cancer;

          -  lesions> 1 cm;

          -  legal capacity to give informed consent in accordance with ICH / EU GCP and national /
             local regulations.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy;

          -  presumed pregnancy;

          -  known coagulation defects;

          -  alcohol or drug abuse
